Note: First four lines may be burden?

CULAdd5943.First Lines:
Pater noster most of myȝtþat al þys world hast wrot
                    wrotehelp me synful wrechyd wyȝtfor synne þat I perytche
                    nowt…
CULAdd5943.Last Lines:
…ffor þyn sone þat deyd on trehelp me wrecche
                    þat y ne spylle
